      <tr><td rowspan="2" class="hl" style="background:#e8f4e8"><strong>Parietal</strong></td><td>Somatosensory Cortex (Post-central Gyrus) ⭐</td><td>Projection area for body senses; proprioception</td><td>Sensory loss, agnosia</td></tr>
