  <div class="callout red"><strong>Triad</strong>: Miosis + Ptosis + Anhidrosis (dry face/skin) → disrupted sympathetic supply. Ptosis = loss of Müller's muscle innervation. Miosis = unopposed parasympathetic.</div>

