<section class="page-section anchor" id="flowcharts">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-tag green">Algorithms</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Quick Flowcharts & Algorithms</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="two-col">
    <div class="algo">
      <h4>⭐ Aphasia Algorithm</h4>
      <div style="font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.8">
        <strong>Step 1: Is speech FLUENT?</strong><br>
        ↳ <span style="color:#8b3a3a">NO (non-fluent):</span><br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;→ Comprehend? YES → Broca's (can't repeat) or Transcortical Motor (can repeat)<br>
